<p class="headline" align="center"><strong>Are                 You Pregnant? Looking For Options?</strong></p>
<p align="center">Whether you just found out you are pregnant, or are late into               your pregnancy, we have information for you. Maybe it\'s               your daughter or girlfriend who just learned she is having               a baby.</p>
<p align="center"><strong>We Can Help You With An Unplanned Pregnancy. </strong></p>
<p align="center">We understand that decisions about a pregnancy               aren\'t always easy. Unplanned or unexpected pregnancies happen,               and helping you make the best decision             for you and your baby is what we are here for.</p>
<p align="center">Click any of the links at the right to learn more               about your options.                Or, call our <strong><br /> 24-Hour              Pregnancy Options Hotline at </strong><span style="font-size: large; font-family: \'comic sans ms\',sans-serif;">1-888-363-1440</span><strong>.</strong></p>
</td>
