<p style="text-align: center; direction: ltr; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; margin: 0; padding: 0;"><span style="color: #ff0000; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 24pt; font-weight: bold;">than<a title="child adoption post placement" href="/administration/childconnect.com"> </a></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center; direction: ltr; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; margin: 0; padding: 0;"><span style="color: #ff0000; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 24pt; font-weight: bold;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a title="child adoption post placement" href="/administration/childconnect.com"><img alt="child adoption post placement" src="http://childconnect.com/images/cclogo.gif" height="65" width="220" /></a></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center; direction: ltr; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; margin: 0; padding: 0;"><span style="color: #ff0000; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 24pt; font-weight: bold;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><br /></span></span></p>
<p style="direction: ltr; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; margin: 0; padding: 0; min-height: 11pt;"><span> </span></p>
<p style="direction: ltr; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; margin: 0; padding: 0;"><span> </span></p>
<p style="direction: ltr; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; margin: 0; padding: 0;"><span> </span></p>
<p style="direction: ltr; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; margin: 0; padding: 0;"><span>Before  ChildConnect.com birth parents were lucky if they received more than a  handful of photos, but with ChildConnect.com birth parents are receiving  more updates and photos than they ever imagined due to the simplicity  and ease of use.  Pictures can be uploaded to the system in minutes to  create beautiful life books.</span></p>
<p style="direction: ltr; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; margin: 0; padding: 0; min-height: 11pt;"><span> </span></p>
<p style="direction: ltr; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; margin: 0; padding: 0;"><span>If  you are in the adoption process, be sure to ask your adoption service  provider if they use ChildConnect.com to handle post-adoption  picture/letter contracts.  If they don&rsquo;t, tell them you want  your adoption contract facilitated through ChildConnect.com.  You can  also search out agencies using ChildConnect.com by submitting an </span><span style="color: #1155cc; text-decoration: underline;"><a href="http://www.google.com/url?q=http%3A%2F%2Fforms.cairsolutions.com%2Fview.php%3Fid%3D23&amp;sa=D&amp;sntz=1&amp;usg=AFQjCNE0K2BsZaYyrJIuRsR4UaKXEZI5PA" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;" target="_blank">inquiry here. </a></span></p>
<p style="direction: ltr; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; margin: 0; padding: 0;"><span style="color: #1155cc; text-decoration: underline;"><br /></span></p>
<p style="direction: ltr; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; margin: 0; padding: 0;"><span style="color: #1155cc; text-decoration: underline;"><a href="http://forms.cairsolutions.com/view.php?id=19"><img alt="post doption pictures and letters contract tool" src="http://www.childconnect.com/images/cc_bparentinq_btn.gif" height="40" width="174" /></a><br /></span></p>
<p style="direction: ltr; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; margin: 0; padding: 0; min-height: 11pt;"><span> </span></p>
<p style="direction: ltr; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; margin: 0; padding: 0;"><span>If  you previously placed a child for adoption and your adoption service  provider did not use Child Connect.com, there is still time to ask for this  service for upcoming updates.</span></p>
<p style="direction: ltr; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; margin: 0; padding: 0; min-height: 11pt;"><span> </span></p>
<p style="direction: ltr; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; margin: 0; padding: 0;"><span>If  you are a birth mother that uses ChildConnect.com, be sure to tell  others.  Also, if you blog, please recommend this tool in your posts.   Adoptive families love the ease of this tool, which means more photos  and updates for birth parents!</span></p>
<p style="direction: ltr; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; margin: 0; padding: 0;">&nbsp;</p>
