<h1><img src="http://www.wordes.org/parentfinder/img/pages/letter_to_expectant_mother/to_the_expectant_mother.png" alt="To the expectant mother&hellip;" /></h1>
<p>During this important decision-making  period, it is important to talk to people who have the experience and  knowledge to support you and your choice, no matter what your choice is.   Whether you are leaning toward parenting, abortion, or adoption, you  should know there are resources available to help and we strongly  encourage talking with someone about your situation and options.</p>
<p>If you are seriously considering adoption  for your child, you should know there are more families seeking to  adopt a child than you probably realize and these families are waiting  and prepared to get to know you better.  You can begin your search  whenever you are ready and trust that ParentFinder.com will connect you  with only approved adoptive families that have undergone an extensive  home study and interview process.</p>
<p>Furthermore, if you aren&rsquo;t already  working with an adoption service provider and would like assistance  along the way, we&rsquo;d be happy to have our adoption specialist contact you  and provide guidance until you are comfortably linked to an adoption  agency or attorney.</p>
